3100.name: Spellbook: Guidance
3100.description: Spellbook needed to learn Guidance. Used by Prophets and Shillien Elders. Required level: 40

3101.name: Spellbook: Death Whisper
3101.description: Spellbook needed to learn Death Whisper. Used by Prophets and Shillien Elders. Required level: 40

3102.name: Spellbook: Bless Shield
3102.description: Spellbook needed to learn Bless Shield. Used by Prophets and Elven Elders. Required level: 40

3103.name: Amulet: Pa'agrio's Wisdom
3103.description: Amulet required for the Pa'agrio's Wisdom spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 40

3104.name: Amulet: Pa'agrio's Glory
3104.description: Amulet required for the Pa'agrio's Glory spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 40

3105.name: Amulet: Seal of Winter
3105.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Winter spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 40

3106.name: Amulet: Seal of Flame
3106.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Flame spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 48

3107.name: Amulet: Seal of Gloom
3107.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Gloom spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 44

3108.name: Amulet: Seal of Mirage
3108.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Mirage spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 44

3109.name: Amulet: Seal of Silence
3109.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Silence spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 48

3110.name: Amulet: Seal of Scourge
3110.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Scourge spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 40

3111.name: Amulet: Seal of Suspension
3111.description: Amulet required for the Seal of Suspension spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 48

3112.name: Amulet: Pa'agrio's Vision
3112.description: Amulet required for the Pa'agrio's Vision spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 44

3113.name: Amulet: Pa'agrio's Protection
3113.description: Amulet required for the Pa'agrio's Protection spell. Used by Overlords. Required level: 40

3114.name: Amulet: Steal Essence
3114.description: Amulet required for the Steal Essence spell. Used by Warcryers and Overlords. Required level: 40

3115.name: Amulet: Freezing Flame
3115.description: Amulet required for the Freezing Flame spell. Used by Warcryers. Required level: 40

3116.name: Amulet: Chant of Fury
3116.description: Amulet required for the Chant of Fury spell. Used by Warcryers. Required level: 48

3117.name: Amulet: Chant of Evasion
3117.description: Amulet required for the Chant of Evasion spell. Used by Warcryers. Required level: 40

3118.name: Amulet: Chant of Rage
3118.description: Amulet required for the Chant of Rage spell. Used by Warcryers. Required level: 44

3119.name: Mark of Guildsman
3119.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Guildsman. An occupation change related item.

3120.name: Valkon's Recommendation
3120.description: A recommendation letter written by Warehouse Keeper Valkon. Take this and go to Blacksmith Altran of Talking Island.

3121.name: Mandragora Berry
3121.description: The fruit of mandragoras, known for their uses in treating ailments.

3122.name: Altran's Instructions
3122.description: Blacksmith Altran's instructions. The instructions are to gather materials and create 7 journeyman's rings.

3123.name: Altran's 1st Recommendation
3123.description: A recommendation letter written by Blacksmith Altran. Take this and go to Warehouse Keeper Norman of the Village of Gludin.

3124.name: Altran's 2nd Recommendation
3124.description: A recommendation letter written by Blacksmith Altran. Take this and go to Blacksmith Pinter of the Town of Gludio.

3125.name: Norman's Instructions
3125.description: Warehouse Keeper Norman's instructions. The instructions are to go to Blacksmith Duning of Hunters Village and bring back the key.

3126.name: Norman's Receipt
3126.description: Warehouse Keeper Norman's receipt. Take this and go to Blacksmith Duning of the Hunters Village.

3127.name: Duning's Instructions
3127.description: Blacksmith Duning's instructions. It gives an order to recover 30 keys from Breka orcs.

3128.name: Duning's Key
3128.description: Mithril key recovered from Breka orcs. Collect 30 and take them to Blacksmith Duning.

3129.name: Norman's List
3129.description: Ingredient list of Warehouse Keeper Norman: 70 units of gray bone powder, 70 granite whetstones, 70 units of red pigment, and 70 units of braided yarn.

3130.name: Gray Bone Powder
3130.description: The powder collected from the bones of ghouls and strains. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.

3131.name: Granite Whetstone
3131.description: A whetstone made from the fragments of the granite golem. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.

3132.name: Red Pigment
3132.description: Red pigment obtained by slaying the dead seeker bat. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.

3133.name: Braided Yarn
3133.description: Braided yarn obtained by slaying the silenos. Gather 70 of these and take them to Warehouse Keeper Norman.

3134.name: Journeyman Gem
3134.description: A material used to make the journeyman's ring.

3135.name: Pinter's Instructions
3135.description: Instructions of Blacksmith Pinter: Find and bring back 70 amber beads.

3136.name: Amber Bead
3136.description: A bead-shaped piece of amber. Collect 70 of these and take them to Blacksmith Pinter.

3137.name: Amber Lump
3137.description: An unrefined lump of amber. The material used in creating the Amber Bead.

3138.name: Journeyman Deco Beads
3138.description: Ingredient item used to make a journeyman's ring.

3139.name: Journeyman Ring
3139.description: To pass the Trial of the Guildsman, you must create 7 of these rings. Take the completed rings to Warehouse Keeper Valkon.

3140.name: Mark of Life
3140.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Life. An occupation change related item.

3141.name: Cardien's Letter
3141.description: Letter by Master Cardien. Take this and go to Hierarch Asterios of the Elven Village.

3142.name: Camomile Charm
3142.description: A talisman given by Hierarch Asterios. Take this and return to Master Cardien in the Town of Dion.

3143.name: Hierarch's Letter
3143.description: A letter given by Hierarch Asterios. Take this and go to Thalia, who lives on the eastern shores of Iris Lake.

3144.name: Moonflower Charm
3144.description: The charm given by Hierarch Asterios to keep in possession while searching for the water of life.

3145.name: Grail Diagram
3145.description: A diagram of the grail, given by Thalia. Take this and go to Blacksmith Pushkin of Town of Giran.

3146.name: Thalia's 1st Letter
3146.description: Thalia's letter. Take this and go to Arkenia, who is at the Altar of Rites.

3147.name: Thalia's 2nd Letter
3147.description: Thalia's letter. Take this and go to Isael Silvershadow of the Hunters Village.

3148.name: Thalia's Instructions
3148.description: A letter containing Thalia's instructions. The instructions are to come back after reaching level 38.

3149.name: Pushkin's List
3149.description: A list given by Blacksmith Pushkin. "10 pure Mithril Ore, 20 ant soldier acid, 20 Wyrm talons"

3150.name: Pure Mithril Cup
3150.description: A cup crafted by Blacksmith Pushkin that is made of pure mithril. Take this back to Thalia.

3151.name: Arkenia's Contract
3151.description: A contract written by Arkenia. The contract states that she will give stardust in return for Andariel's book from the Village of Gludin.

3152.name: Arkenia's Instructions
3152.description: Arkenia's instructions. The instructions are to bring back Andariel's book from the Temple of Einhasad in the Village of Gludin.

3153.name: Adonius's list
3153.description: A list given by Priest Adonius: 20 spider ichor and 20 harpy's down.

3154.name: Andariel Scripture Copy
3154.description: A copy of Andariel's book given by Priest Adonius. Take this back to Arkenia.

3155.name: Stardust
3155.description: The silver dust received from Arkenia of the Dark Elves. Take this back to Thalia.

3156.name: Isael's Instructions
3156.description: A document containing Isael Silvershadow's instructions. It asks you to recover 6 pieces of talins spear from Leto lizardman shamans.

3157.name: Isael's Letter
3157.description: A letter given by Isael Silvershadow. Take this back to Thalia along with Talin's spear.

3158.name: Grail of Purity
3158.description: A grail crafted of pure mithril. Catch the tears of the unicorn with the grail and take it back to Thalia.

3159.name: Tears of Unicorn
3159.description: The tears shed by Eva's unicorn when it is killed with Talin's spear. Take this back to Thalia.

3160.name: Water of Life
3160.description: The holy water that contains the powers of life to rejuvenate the Mother Tree. Take this and go to Hierarch Asterios.

3161.name: Pure Mithril Ore
3161.description: The ore of pure mithril. Gather 10 of these, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.

3162.name: Ant Soldier Acid
3162.description: The acid collected from ant soldiers after slaying them. Gather 20 bottles of this, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.

3163.name: Wyrm's Talon
3163.description: The talon of a Wyrm obtained after slaying it. Gather 20 of these, along with the rest of the ingredients, and take them back to Blacksmith Pushkin.

3164.name: Spider Ichor
3164.description: The ichor of a marsh spider. Gather 20 units of this and take them back to Priest Adonius.

3165.name: Harpy's Down
3165.description: The down feathers obtained after slaying a harpy. Gather 20 of these and take them back to Priest Adonius.

3166.name: Talin's Spear Blade
3166.description: The blade portion of Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3167.name: Talin's Spear Shaft
3167.description: The shaft portion of Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3168.name: Talin's Ruby
3168.description: A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3169.name: Talin's Aquamarine
3169.description: A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3170.name: Talin's Amethyst
3170.description: A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3171.name: Talin's Peridot
3171.description: A decorative jewel that adorned Talin's spear. Take this, along with the remaining portions of the spear, back to Isael Silvershadow.

3172.name: Mark of Fate
3172.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Testimony of Fate. An item for occupational change.

3173.name: Kaira's Letter
3173.description: A letter sent by Magister Kaira to Brother Metheus of the Temple of Einhasad. This must be delivered secretly.

3174.name: Metheus's Funeral Jar
3174.description: A jar for storing the remains of the dead. Take this to the Execution Grounds and search for the remains of Metheus's sister.

3175.name: Kasandra's Remains
3175.description: The remains of Kasandra, Metheus's sister. Take this back to Brother Metheus.

3176.name: Herbalism Textbook
3176.description: A textbook of various herbs and their usages. It also contains information about the deadly poison belladonna.

3177.name: Ixia's List
3177.description: 10 units each of medusa's blood, marsh spider fluids, dead seeker's dung, tyrant's blood and nightshade root.

3178.name: Medusa's Ichor
3178.description: The bottled blood of a medusa. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia

3179.name: Marsh Spider's Fluids
3179.description: The bottled fluids of a marsh spider. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.

3180.name: Dead Seeker Dung
3180.description: The dung of dead seeker bats. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.

3181.name: Tyrant's Blood
3181.description: The bottled blood of tyrant. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.

3182.name: Nightshade Root
3182.description: The roots of the rare nightshade herb. Collect 10 of these and take them back to Master Ixia.

3183.name: Belladonna
3183.description: A legendary poison that can kill a bull with a single drop. Take this to Brother Metheus.

3184.name: Alder's Skull
3184.description: The skull of Alders, who drafted the copy of Kaysha's Revelations. Take this to Magister Kaira.

3185.name: Alders Skull
3185.description: Skull of Priest Alders. Take it to Magister Roa, a distant descendant of the priest.

3186.name: Alder's Receipt
3186.description: The receipt for the item that Alder entrusted to the warehouse. Take this and go to the warehouse in the Village of Gludin.

3187.name: Revelations Manuscript
3187.description: A copy of Kaysha's Revelations. Take this to Magister Kaira.

3188.name: Kaira's Instructions
3188.description: A note where Magister Kaira's instructions are written. The instructions are to come back after reaching level 38.

3189.name: Kaira's Recommendation
3189.description: A recommendation letter written by Magister Kaira. Take this and go to Tetrarch Thifiell of the Dark Elven Village.

3190.name: Palus Charm
3190.description: A charm given by Tetrarch Thifiell to keep in possession until the Initiation Ceremony of the Shillien Circle is complete.

3191.name: Thifiell's Letter
3191.description: A letter from Tetrarch Thifiell to Arkenia. Arkenia is at the Dark Elven Initiation Altar.

3192.name: Arkenia's Note
3192.description: A note written by Arkenia. It contains instructions to bring back red fairy dust and blight treant sap.

3193.name: Pixy Garnet
3193.description: A garnet given by the Bloody Pixy as a token of promise. Bring one skull each of four different races.

3194.name: Grandis' Skull
3194.description: The skull of Grandis. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.

3195.name: Karul Bugbear Skull
3195.description: The skull of Karul Bugbear. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.

3196.name: Breka Overlord Skull
3196.description: The skull of a Breka Overlord. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.

3197.name: Leto Overlord Skull
3197.description: The skull of a Leto Lizardman Overlord. Bring this to the Bloody Pixy.

3198.name: Red Fairy Dust
3198.description: Red fairy dust given by the bloody pixy. Take this to Arkenia.

3199.name: Blight Treant Seed
3199.description: A seed given by a blight treant as a mark of promise. Slay the black willow lurker and bring back its leaf.
